## What is this?

The Compound Engine is my public engineering journey.

This repository is where I consistently document:

- Things I learn
- Projects I build
- Daily progress
- Coding practice
- DSA
- SQL
- AI & Machine Learning
- Data Engineering
- Experiments
- Research
- Ideas
- Lessons learned

This is not a repository of perfect work.

It is a repository of continuous growth.

